@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082
@token = replace-with-login-access-token

### 1. 初始化库存 - 正常
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/init
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 1,
  "stock_quantity": 100
}

### 2. 初始化库存 - 不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/init
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 999,
  "stock_quantity": 100
}

### 3. 初始化库存 - `stock_quantity = 0` 可以初始化
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/init
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 1,
  "stock_quantity": 0
}

### 4. 增加库存 - 正常
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 1,
  "quantity": 20
}

### 5. 增加库存 - 未初始化库存，应失败
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 2,
  "quantity": 0
}

### 6. 增加库存 - quantity <= 0,应失败
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 1,
  "quantity": -1
}

### 7. 查询商品库存
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 查询商品库存 - 非法 product_id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/products/abc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 查询商品库存 - 不存在
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/products/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
